loopjefe-lv2 (1.0.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial package. Forked from mod-audio/sooperlooper-lv2-plugin
    (itself derived from Jesse Chappell's SooperLooper). Adds beat-synced
    (bar-quantized) recording via the LV2 time extension and a single-CC
    5-state cycle (state/reset control ports, replacing the old
    play_pause/record pair) for the pi-Stomp multitrack looper workflow.
    Ships both the mono (loopjefe) and stereo (loopjefe-2x2) bundles.

